{"tid":1387410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人！我地無下次架啦！！！！It's now or never！！！！","createTime":"2019-07-30T13:56:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T23:21:39.000Z","uid":286758,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"de6630890cc7f1f9b05b617092ab92956991af82","tid":1387410,"uid":286758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:56:01.000Z","msg":"P牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n我dllm d post個個係到講咩陪審團、留得青山在！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地無下次架啦！！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">底線一次又一次咁退，一次又一次寄望下一個stage下一個stage，我地有幾多個stage退啊？？？？？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">執法信唔過！！！</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">司法信得過咩？？？</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你信咩L樣都唔知嘅陪審團！！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n你係咪要學番我地上一代，將個問題留比5年後、10年後、20年後嘅後生仔，然後自我感覺良好自己當年盡左力啦。5年後、10年後、20年後，當d後生仔問番我地宜家嘅問題：<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">爸爸媽媽，點解當年你唔幫我地爭取一個更好嘅生活？？</span></strong></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">爸爸媽媽，當年爭取嘅時候你去左做咩？？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">你點答？？？？？？？？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你覺得我地仲會有下次咩？？？？？？？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">魚革拉咗64人，反修例到依家拉左18x人。你係咪想下一代比人拉幾百人，甚至幾千人，坐番357年，由佢地去支付你今日不作為的代價？？？？？？？？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你都行左99.99999%，無理由宜家縮番去個鴕鳥洞啊？？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n工我會罷，行我會繼續行，會我會繼續集。投降只會令政府不用付出任何代價地平息事態，係向政府<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">示弱</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>示完L弱，你覺得香港人仲會有活路嗎？？？？？？？？？</strong></span><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>示完L弱，你覺得政府唔會食住上嗎？？？？？？？？？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你係咪要係仲有餘力嘅情況之下投降？？？？？？</span></span></strong><br />\n（題外：我唔鼓勵大家送頭，我認同要轉換抗爭方法）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我地無下次架啦！</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無下次架啦！</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無下次啊！！！！！！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">It's now or never</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"00d9e03d01d36d87d89d2f47cd124d5b3f7876ba","tid":1387410,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905e936f41df28036d13df411880d8ea8d729a05","tid":1387410,"uid":160176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:01:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b9273901fcf34b9b9a6cf7a4e09104f3064ba5c","tid":1387410,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vYbFFgJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvYbFFgJ.png&h=5dfe1d38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77a12ae7ac0a029c11f50abe5a6cdc6e7f2e65d4","tid":1387410,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:11:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f11017e2a15f7460834f283ef10a6a439e4e5cd3"